-- Monte Paschi sets initial guidance on 7-yr covered bond-source
-- By Valentina Za
-- Thu Apr 10, 2014 03:23AM EDT
-- None



MILAN, April 10 (Reuters) - Banca Monte dei Paschi di Siena <BMPS.MI> has set at around 175 basis points over the relevant mid-swap rate the initial yield guidance on a seven-year covered bond, a source close to the deal said on Thursday.

